Class ListNode<E>

java.lang.Object
  dat1.ListNode<E>

public class ListNode<E>
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a node (or entry) in a LinkedList.

Each ListNode can be linked to a next and a previous ListNode. Those are the nodes that will come immediately before and after it in a LinkedList.

Author:
K. Atas
